#=== README ===#

backup.sh is simple script.

Dependencies:
  * rdiff-backup
  * posix-sh

Configuration:
  Is simple (i think) in script file.

  exclude - define what places rdiff-backup have to exclude
  o_opt - other options
  b_dir - directory to backup
  d_dir - destination of backup
  log - where save logs
  disc - partition needed to mount to make backup

